'''Abby''' is a child who got separated from her mother during a parking garage fire.

==History==
Abby and her brother, [[Jonny]], were out with their mother when she stopped at a grocery store to get chocolate milk. She left Abby and Jonny in the car while she went inside. While she was gone, a fire started in the parking garage. When Jonny was rendered unconscious, Abby struggled to wake him so they could get away from the fire. She was trying to pull him out when [[Ben Warren|Ben]] and [[Victoria Hughes|Vic]] found them and got them out to safety. Jonny was loaded onto a gurney and he and Abby were taken to the hospital.

==Relationships==
===Familial===
She lives with her mom and her brother, [[Jonny]].
